# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:822
msgid ""
"The Deinterlace effect is used to remove interlacing artifacts from video "
"footage, which are commonly seen as horizontal lines across moving objects. "
"This effect is essential for converting interlaced video (such as from older "
"video cameras or broadcast sources) into a progressive format suitable for "
"modern displays."
