# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:837
msgid ""
"The Hue effect adjusts the overall color balance of the video, changing the "
"hues without affecting the brightness or saturation. This can be used for "
"color correction or to apply dramatic color effects that transform the mood "
"of the footage."
msgstr ""
"تأثير الصبغة يضبط التوازن اللوني العام للفيديو، مغيرًا الصبغات دون التأثير "
